# Data — ignored by default. Audit / discovery CSVs in data/reports/ are
# the exception: small, version-controlled snapshots that feed gap-analysis
# sprints. Use `data/*` (not `data/`) so git can still descend into data/
# and discover the un-ignored reports subdirectory.
data/*
!data/reports/
packages/ingest/data/

